173
00:22:51,440 --> 00:22:55,450
(Student ID: Yun I Seo)

174
00:23:00,450 --> 00:23:01,690
It's because of me.

175
00:23:03,550 --> 00:23:05,790
It's my fault this happened to I Seo.

176
00:23:10,560 --> 00:23:12,530
Can you tell me...

177
00:23:13,760 --> 00:23:15,630
