179
00:23:20,700 --> 00:23:21,770
Hey, I Seo.

180
00:23:24,470 --> 00:23:25,980
This is so much fun.

181
00:23:26,440 --> 00:23:28,450
- You gotta try this. - What is it?

182
00:23:28,680 --> 00:23:32,250
