183
00:23:32,920 --> 00:23:36,320
- I'm not really good at games. - This one's super easy.

184
00:23:37,090 --> 00:23:41,160
I have to see a teacher. Play for me? I'll be right back.

185
00:23:47,700 --> 00:23:49,430
(Odd)

